title: [Teiya's General Store]
[Teiya's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a mosaic tiled ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the textured sandstone walls.  A glass-topped mistwood counter and a plain wooden table sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on a sturdy planked floor.

Beneath a mosaic tiled ceiling, a snarling troll king mask hangs on one of the textured sandstone walls.  A glass-topped mistwood counter and a plain wooden table sit in opposite corners while a carved ebonwood dinghy rests on a sturdy planked floor.
